# Legacy website — no polish

These paths are the **preserved Next.js website** under `/legacy`.

- Do **not** add features or polish UI here for “parity” with the Expo app.
- The primary web product is the Expo SPA at the domain root.
- Touches are allowed only when needed for routing/domain wiring (e.g. `legacyPath` hrefs).

See `.cursor/rules/app-only-scope.mdc` and `docs/react-native/WEB-DOMAIN.md`.
